title: Strukt - Resurrected [MP3 320kbps / Trance]
description:
Hi,

My name is Bjoernar Kibsgaard and i make music as a hobby. I dont consider myself as a professional or anything like that but i have sold a few downloads of my songs through iTunes.

I have always felt that people should decide themselves if they feel the music is worth paying for or not.

So here you go, my first album "Strukt - Resurrected" in 320kbps crispy quality MP3 for free.

I also included a bonus track, just for you guys !.

Enjoy.

And by the way, if you in some way want to support me, you could search for "Strukt - Resurrected" in iTunes store, or amazon.com. But that is of course your choice, i dont really care :)
